1
00:00:01,883 --> 00:00:05,217
The Absolute Truth
is not Kṛṣṇa alone.

2
00:00:05,217 --> 00:00:07,773
But it’s Rādhā and Kṛṣṇa.

3
00:00:08,745 --> 00:00:11,801
But we’re duped into thinking,

4
00:00:13,187 --> 00:00:15,514
that by the direct approach

5
00:00:15,514 --> 00:00:18,466
we’ll get the superior experience

6
00:00:18,466 --> 00:00:24,665
than serving his agent or agency.

7
00:00:25,188 --> 00:00:27,776
Kṛṣṇa’s Better Half

8
00:00:28,502 --> 00:00:31,915
So, we have to be educated. 

9
00:00:32,331 --> 00:00:35,503
‘rasa-rāja’, ‘mahābhāva’—
dui eka rūpa (Cc: Madhya, 8.282)

10
00:00:35,549 --> 00:00:38,645
mahābhāva-svarūpiṇī
[svarūpā śrī]-rādhā-ṭhākurāṇī (Cc: Ādi, 4.69)

11
00:00:38,645 --> 00:00:40,317
She can extract,

12
00:00:40,317 --> 00:00:43,602
she is the predominated half of Kṛṣṇa,

13
00:00:43,602 --> 00:00:45,110
Kṛṣṇa’s better half.

14
00:00:45,110 --> 00:00:49,520
She can extract
the highest quality

15
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:53,374
and highest quantity 
of rāsa from Kṛṣṇa.

16
00:00:54,004 --> 00:00:56,847
And, hlādinī-śakti puṣṭi kara,

17
00:00:56,847 --> 00:01:02,438
and nourish her servitors 
with that substance.

18
00:01:03,365 --> 00:01:06,140
And Guru Mahārāj said,

19
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:09,018
once you’ve had a taste of that,

20
00:01:09,018 --> 00:01:12,831
mahābhāva, which is beyond 
the constitutional capacity

21
00:01:12,831 --> 00:01:14,703
of a jīva-soul to experience,

22
00:01:14,703 --> 00:01:17,661
Rādhārāṇī out of gratitude
to her servitors

23
00:01:17,661 --> 00:01:19,176
gives them a taste.

24
00:01:19,176 --> 00:01:21,905
once you’ve had a taste of that,

25
00:01:21,905 --> 00:01:23,775
what to speak of all other taste.

26
00:01:23,775 --> 00:01:28,935
All other rāsas, become tasteless.

